<Class name="SpoolerServer" id="6c29411e-1a4b-4dcc-bb82-280dc652c80f">
    <superclass name="Spooler"/>
    <transient/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>PURPOSE:
========
	
	Handles Inwards FTP files by executing spoolAFile method() (user-reimplemented).
	Handles standing Jobs containing Batches of files to be sent Outwards.
	Handles one-time GUI FTP jobs entered via FTP Job Definition and Maintenance 
	(FtpJobMaint form).

	SpoolerServer application must reside on the FTP Server.
	
	See FtpCopyServer for means of getting Application files from
	the Application environment to the FTP server directories.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="FtpData"/>
